    "description": "<p><strong>Maneuver: (1 AP) </strong>Choose a creature that can see or hear you within 5 Spaces. Make an <strong>Attack Check</strong> or <strong>Intimidation Check </strong>(your choice) contested by the target’s <strong>Mental Save</strong>. </p><p><strong>Contest Success:</strong> The target is <strong>Taunted </strong>(DisADV on Attack and Spell Checks against creatures other than you) by you on their next <strong>Attack </strong>or <strong>Spell Check</strong>.</p><p><strong>Full Taunt:</strong> You can spend an additional <strong>1 AP</strong> to have the <strong>Taunted </strong>Condition last until the end of your next turn.</p><p></p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> By default this item is configured to use <strong>Attack Check</strong>. You need to edit \"Roll\" Tab to change it to <strong>Intimidation Check</strong>.</em></p>",
